{"id": "duc04-testb-44:6#18", "contents": "Lucia Pinochet, the wife of former Chilean dictator Augusto Pinochet, has made an emotional appeal for her husband's release from arrest. Speaking to reporters outside the London Clinic where Pinochet is recuperating from back surgery, she expressed her family's pain and asked for compassion for her ailing husband. Pinochet, 82, underwent surgery on October 9 for a herniated disc and has been arrested since October 16, pending extradition to Spain to face charges of genocide, terrorism, and torture."}
